| SubmitTrigger | `SubmitTrigger` | `SubmitTrigger` | Full parity                                           |
| CancelTrigger | `CancelTrigger` | `CancelTrigger` | Full parity                                           |
| Area          | --              | `Area`          | Ark wraps Input+Preview; ars-ui Root serves this role |
